WEBVTT

00:12:28.860 --> 00:12:33.301
and seeing their own country
with fresh eyes.

00:12:33.325 --> 00:12:34.982
And they see what's going on.

00:12:35.738 --> 00:12:37.593
This is the country they fought for.

00:12:38.433 --> 00:12:40.111
No wonder they're depressed.

00:12:40.135 --> 00:12:41.709
No wonder they're scared.

00:12:43.371 --> 00:12:47.248
Sometimes, we ask ourselves
if we can save the vets.

00:12:48.248 --> 00:12:51.418
I think the real question
is if we can save ourselves.

00:12:51.905 --> 00:12:53.595
If we can,

00:12:53.619 --> 00:12:55.593
I think the vets are going to be fine.

00:12:56.697 --> 00:12:59.834
It's time for this country to unite,